Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:36.16,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}嘴上總是試圖用　言遮掩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:36.16,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\fscx103\fscy103\pos(1046,12)}謊
