Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.01,0:23:26.97,ED-11-CH,,0,0,0,,Romantic 戀愛的天線
Dialogue: 1,0:23:27.43,0:23:32.39,ED-11-CH,,0,0,0,,{\c&HF4A510&}在風雨中被吹去了別處
